window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>I conquered the land. I saw its potential. I won the Wild Sorceress. Now, I must establish my power.</b></p> <p>From my new castle in Northshire, I watch my two cities thrive, fueled by magic and ambition. I’ve overcome overwhelming odds and earned the loyalty of powerful allies. But with powerful allies come greater dangers.</p> <p>My neighbors fall to monster attacks. Whispers of sapient creatures digging beneath the land grow louder. In the tunnels under my home, ancient secrets stir, and an old power—buried for millennia—calls to me with hatred, threatening to destroy my hard work.</p> <p>Victory is no longer enough. Now, I must secure my legacy.</p> <p>I’ll conquer again.</p> <p>I’ll win again.</p> <p><b>As many times as it takes.</b></p>"; 
